qtglassflow (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * SDF-based superellipse glass shapes with smooth-union sticky bridging.
  * Real-time refraction, convex dome lighting, and sub-pixel anti-aliasing.
  * Interactive demo with parameter tuning panel.

